Name: Clutter VI: Leigh's Story
About the game: The best Clutter yet by far. With Leigh's Story, the Clutter series has risen to a whole new level. For the first time, there is a compelling story with gameplay to match. Additionally, many new Clutter styles of play have been added, including, 'Head To Head', 'Clutter Chaos' and 'Twos & Threes'. There is truly something here for everyone. All your old favorites are back as well and there are more Clutter 100 levels in Leigh's Story, than ever before. Features: Over 500 New Objects Over 800 Levels Over 20 hours of Gameplay 75+ Picture Puzzles, 75+ Box Quotes Puzzles Randomly generated levels provide hours and hours of replayability
